  "bio_raw": "Suravi Akhter has been serving as a Lecturer in the Department of Computer science and Engineering (CSE). She received her BSc. and MSc degree in Software Engineering from the Institute of Information Technology, University of Dhaka, Dhaka, Bangladesh in 2019 and 2022. Her major research interests include Machine Learning, Data Science and Natural Language Processing.",
